snippet.title: God Saves - Texas AMBER Alert (EAS #134) [Re-Uploaded]
snippet.description:
The child was found safe not long after the AMBER Alert was issued.

This video was Re-Uploaded to fix errors.



BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
650 PM CDT WED JUN 10 2020

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT
NETWORK

THE MATHIS POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR ENRIQUE HERNANDEZ,
HISPANIC, MALE, 5 YEARS OLD, HEIGHT 3 FEET 11 INCHES, WEIGHT 80 
POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, AND BROWN EYES.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR STEPHANIE OLIVAREZ, HISPANIC, FEMALE, 22 YEARS
OLD, HEIGHT 5 FEET 6 INCHES, WEIGHT 223 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, AND 
BROWN EYES, IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A RED, 2002, DODGE, NEON WITH A TX, LICENSE
PLATE NUMBER OF * * * * * * *.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN MATHIS, TX.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER. 

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE MATHIS
POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 361 547-2113.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS MATHIS POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 361
547-2113.

$$

Intro and Outro Music:
Entering Gracefully - LIMO Recording Studio
